&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i85Yr.4XnxQM/v0/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;现场问答：伊朗战争会促进清洁技术投资吗？&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;自去年以来，清洁能源股的涨幅超过了标准普尔 500 指数，公共和私人对绿色初创企业的投资也大幅增长，今年第一季度达到 225 亿美元。这一切都是在伊朗战争导致油价飙升之前发生的。在特朗普政府的政策和全球气候进展停滞的情况下，投资者和公司将资金押注在哪里？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;与彭博社记者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kQM-nDQkCasdshk54ghtRpZbIrKfMfxQrqOzff79pbf10S_yGij72HUYw-MWv2C_hmilZXetvgh8kkc_N_drbgk0il2bL4beCKlEEHJExg6OpytzFTnBDlHAR-vax3ZaN1N6O2qrTKX1t5ji4h3WpwWhBOIuJVDfTiBaPhzAuLsfuRoudPDkLseM1Vysm6vXmyHBNTjToPpnVlF20Mng_L6LVl_esRhuewoG_JNJ6Pjo6X7V88dabji9Y-a8iCEAS8KBsxkoqlZ2PLRRZRZbUATDNQRvc8Pzj3tlon0xfroV6GbsXIZZRE-EyBMsMaTCZNh5FBav3g/0h2qSuCoU2cVcRRWTB8TRtVaJEh73-Fx/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Akshat Rathi - 高级记者：气候 |布隆伯格"&gt;Akshat Rathi&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dE1U61U-manqZpjMtaHfbzQpyTMKNqzuCXqELpxmxmH_iudmj389yWPzYBuFePCSWz1N-BFEcKDKhjsnlH37W7GpjPQzZ6RX75_OLmPNl369MtY1QvUhEHfY_doYJd7cc7ZMVM6pz3j5qtvIogVkTD7lQpV1O_F_uEBiRwtJQSYZHFfUdHvkGgJOK7NOa4Z9bC7a-w7Wm5y2WsMTNJyX0trFA6J5ov5T_4bF_f18VFYS-uQ9Xh3uU1NHZmZL8QdIWwjwVvsomIxHaOq82_2pF9HBAkpS_Nv-8a9_yQls3T-ak0cGHc8c5Gy2FkJtgKVPDIvLxW5uYTQh/Qe5mjh2Vw1CW_Gm-jFdAlrp58ju4WyzK/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="阿拉斯泰尔·马什 - 记者 |布隆伯格"&gt;Alastair Marsh&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zXsUYbLtMsjmliUxmm3eh9aqFJKLke5cLmaXe8fgKiHwTPisi3Nfb6sgIoaeAky1bk69LlMR8bz2-Imn5NTNU42YoUrOj0w0fmaV1HF36mSAh5rDl_C1mV4cKZyDYT5o0pcTjqVGe_oSOd0ddyhjK-23G9DMw3q84eP5XpE