进行自然资源买卖交易。现在，特朗普正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/k1e4o3y_u7GQbHkWZsRLoSJfJUQ9_4u9iyWOQ8tbTt2rMDwjlUfwiWU9FLrIpkoUGamzLoDTzQvD28j4vH6PuamMtBEE_rQ8jrp4n2Gct6uhl6YBJnKiDSOVz3DoekZ8xKpC7KaotYW1Spilfu5RXoBm31NmDZO89TkhCfP2AVnBPQYP4WYRH__Mcj9D3ntLqmGA14DMlbhdgPXyH3RIYvGnL4Djoar2vmJxdLNdptc7kFdTYb3vFspZ7qz-UWrdHBGJ8SI6DWHUQgygPaw_RUESIPYq3Bogk7-gxl7YMSjVN43t3qZSgMLu6zxM2wISeBOCi1mphJ1uRdqLvtWTlk56f4uS6Jmfzk-hm_js1bnPGaRJqtJyQSm-hmA1Fd3UMLX6xO-0sh3OfFo_b6CgEB8QgvU5NEg58jgMGaIeJm1NC4vN8NIUtu1S1OKWt_WHEWTdAiqBa7pzWwMheymqK2DPTrcfAY2bsrcb-k21aw8_nov4znhb81RkReNaI8EcwwzQy8K41Iqw331y-AzZpaDaOJ0PjRYt/6Sq9ThqrHAZmSMNQ9Egz3_gLuaJYYUu1/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="长期回避政治后，大宗商品交易商开始向特朗普示好"&gt;改变游戏规则&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;近几个月来，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国政府&lt;/strong&gt;更深入地进行大宗商品交易，授予合同或合作伙伴关系，这些合同或合作伙伴关系可能对参与者来说利润丰厚。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;当特朗普在取代委内瑞拉总统的军事行动后需要&lt;/strong&gt;迅速从委内瑞拉运出石油时，他呼吁维多和托克提供帮助，为他们提供可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Y6kQ6oXtgTwg4kF301qGyC3cw3Snwf0QlB5_vjNogLqWaMMch-sUIPbu2-Wo_jKh3a4HsUPTC5lnPdM4RNsGn2TXiO2tGNwPpnqqNe0bogMm4s_9dLlpgCUF4TTeJdpHgNVCWVFfygqzKdL7F1vgS7zDAOFP0cd2KE8kmt385OYu4IlEIo5HGS-ualKc6SBb0jX1aiFTq0peMbQQoYwMXK8ebwfqcexuyxnzz-hF3BTGiVcUcpjk5s4LCHMm0EEZ-K0T35fushio_7sUQz-rx0SSo8vze3MsOx1fFJc2PHLj21E3DPnuq2i5Fcqd_4LKcrJJL2DtKtEPme7fdxcm2-UcW-o8axZxnbfjkTY9qeeFdqDiTegAbW1NfE3QJuDtGzK5kLSJZPLe-ahxB95VLgVnI3lkLTsc2bH07m6Zw4G6guEzNeurwTsXmScNmhdF4QRsNg3bTU2FI_1-9CHWDwqkzAafaOZK2hFKbib_YAzQvyy6spFQWiwVnqKl5jLFYK0ACb9SRtbl8r6J2swjjw2VM0mPDlRWpMq3NWB5jw/HybfKBuMO-hFmGJpaLsbtnGAl97Rywdj/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blan